{"tid":2355282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"魯迅曾說，不在沉默中爆發，就在沉默中滅亡","createTime":"2021-01-06T04:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:53:11.000Z","uid":230104,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"241b62581ee3c08ea9cc877a500e1836d1317b09","tid":2355282,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"有一句老話說，沒有傘的孩子唯有拚命奔跑。如果是你，在遭遇狂風暴雨的時候，是選擇找一處屋檐暫時躲避，還是選擇迎着風雨抓緊前行呢？大多數人的選擇都是前者，只有少數人選擇了後者。那少數人這樣說：「既然選擇了遠方，便只顧風雨兼程。」<br />\n<br />\n就如同生活一般，當災厄來臨了，你是選擇逃避還是選擇勇敢面對呢？魯迅曾說，不在沉默中爆發，就在沉默中滅亡。想要收穫成功與幸福，就要勇敢反抗。請記住，奔跑，是最有希望的姿態。世界上的所有事，最怕的就是「拚命努力」四個字。這世上的也唯有夢想和幸福不會對任何人設限，只要你不畫地為牢，就永遠有欣賞不完的風景。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJeGRPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJeGRPm.jpg&h=72ff9094&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBpcd2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBpcd2H.jpg&h=33bfb06c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"340dd9902412a68ac94f2ace6fa1eaa787cde11a","tid":2355282,"uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"你地可以選擇移民，但更多人選擇反擊"},{"pid":"42bcba26155680e38a38d62fb42db335532c5b97","tid":2355282,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92kZDza.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92kZDza.gif&h=7385d512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bef381b89c469fca53e6f5365ae439178bc0b0eb","tid":2355282,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42bcba26155680e38a38d62fb42db335532c5b97","tid":2355282,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92kZDza.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92kZDza.gif&h=7385d512&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"又唔好笑佢地，各有各想法"},{"pid":"59d8ab03038d0bb94c1faee88c62ee77c3f42050","tid":2355282,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"340dd9902412a68ac94f2ace6fa1eaa787cde11a","tid":2355282,"uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"你地可以選擇移民，但更多人選擇反擊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"選擇反擊嘅人反擊未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03e7abd0d2eff0282a476e48763fc51d581faac","tid":2355282,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8415feff5f3f1998c47802323b2625c9fc66b53","tid":2355282,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adc7fa27aa5547a0153c2653ccd6cdf2fd3d7bd2","tid":2355282,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}